="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#!/bin/sh</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 脚本目录</span></span><br><span class="line">DIR=$(<span class="built_in">cd</span> `dirname <span class="variable">$0</span>`; <span class="built_in">pwd</span>)</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># git 仓库路径</span></span><br><span class="line">GIT_DIR=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;DIR&#125;</span>/git/仓库"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"脚本路径===========<span class="variable">$&#123;DIR&#125;</span>"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"git仓库路径 ===============<span class="variable">$&#123;GIT_DIR&#125;</span>"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">" - git update <span class="variable">$&#123;GIT_DIR&#125;</span>"</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [ -d <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;GIT_DIR&#125;</span>"</span> ]; <span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;GIT_DIR&#125;</span>"</span></span><br><span class="line">        git checkout <span class="built_in">test</span></span><br><span class="line">        git pull</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">" - module dir is empty!"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">exit</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"==============开始打war包==============="</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># gradle 打包路径</span></span><br><span class="line">SERVER_WAR=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;GIT_DIR&#125;</span>/service"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;SERVER_WAR&#125;</span>"</span></span><br><span class="line">gradle clean build</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">BUILD_PATH=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;SERVER_WAR&#125;</span>/project.war"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [ ! -e <span class="variable">$&#123;BUILD_PATH&#125;</span> ]; <span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">" - the build <span class="variable">$&#123;BUILD_PATH&#125;</span> not find ! "</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">exit</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># WAR包路径</span></span><br><span class="line">PATH_TO_WAR=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;DIR&#125;</span>/warfile"</span></span><br><span class="line">PATH_TO_WAR_FILE=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR&#125;</span>/project.war"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"=================开始复制war包到<span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR&#125;</span>=========="</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [ ! -d <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR&#125;</span> ]; <span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">        mkdir -p <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR&#125;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [ -f <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR_FILE&#125;</span> ]; <span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"===========删除原war包=========="</span></span><br><span class="line">      rm -rf <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR_FILE&#125;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#备份的上一个文件</span></span><br><span class="line">PATH_TO_WAR_FILE_BACK=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR&#125;</span>/project_back.war"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [ -f <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR_FILE_BACK&#125;</span> ]; <span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"===========删除上一个备份的包=========="</span></span><br><span class="line">     rm -rf <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR_FILE_BACK&#125;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [ -f <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR_FILE&#125;</span> ]; <span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"===========备份war包=========="</span></span><br><span class="line">     mv <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR_FILE&#125;</span> <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR&#125;</span>/project_back.war"</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cp <span class="variable">$&#123;BUILD_PATH&#125;</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;PATH_TO_WAR_FILE&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"=============杀死tomcat进程=========="</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">KILL_NAME=<span class="string">"tomcat-15"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ID=`ps -ef | grep <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$KILL_NAME</span>"</span> | grep -v <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$0</span>"</span> | grep -v <span class="string">"grep"</span> | awk <span class="string">'&#123;print $2&#125;'</span>`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"=========进程<span class="variable">$&#123;ID&#125;</span>========="</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> id <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="variable">$ID</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">do</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">kill</span> -9 <span class="variable">$id</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"============killed <span class="variable">$id</span>========"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">done</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"===========启动tomcat=========="</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TOMCAT1=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;DIR&#125;</span>/tomcat-15100/bin"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;TOMCAT1&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">./startup.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"==========<span class="variable">$&#123;TOMCAT1&#125;</span>启动中==========="</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TOMCAT2=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;DIR&#125;</span>/tomcat-15200/bin"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;TOMCAT2&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">./startup.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"==========<span class="variable">$&#123;TOMCAT2&#125;</span>启动中==========="</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">TOMCAT3=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;DIR&#125;</span>/tomcat-15300/bin"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;TOMCAT3&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">./startup.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"==========<span class="variable">$&#123;TOMCAT3&#125;</span>启动中==========="</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"==========脚本执行完毕============"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#tomcat 相关配置</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;Connector port=<span class="string">"15100"</span> redirectPort=<span class="string">"15102"</span> connectionTimeout=<span class="string">"20000"</span> protocol=<span class="string">"HTTP/1.1"</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;Host name=<span class="string">"localhost"</span> autoDeploy=<span class="string">"true"</span> unpackWARs=<span class="string">"true"</span> appBase=<span class="string">"webapps"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;Context reloadable=<span class="string">"true"</span> docBase=<span class="string">"/opt/warfile/padproject.war"</span> path=<span class="string">""</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/Host&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="服务器配置目录">服务器配置目录</h5><p><img src="https://images.adyan.xyz/dir.jpg" alt="服务器配置目录图片"></p><blockquote><p>脚本中使用了三个点的Tomcat。所以只要配置好三个点的tomcat就行了。<br>本次记录与实际工作中的一些经验。当然，本脚本并非原创。只是为了方便后面使用。<br>有幸能看到这个脚本的大佬，可以提一点意见，将其优化一下。使其使用更为方便。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
